bac5212cde33e194fa64","tid":1082531,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:38:58.000Z","msg":"係有分別"},{"pid":"10bdf21174dd18791073f502a81ffdb385eaf778","tid":1082531,"uid":21149,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:41:20.000Z","msg":"電莖rgb燈 -200ms<br />\n電莖logo信仰 -200ms<br />\n電莖套裝加成 -500ms(每件)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e449e9bc511dd63535f980f48b32a18a75877383","tid":1082531,"uid":49136,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"因為人地有錢去追求完美<br />\n個個都求撚其 可能今日仲係56k上網"},{"pid":"fa599e564cd9b9fbf49b18a42b8dc20c1493b373","tid":1082531,"uid":140454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"個個毒撚都以為自己係電競師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1a4b1017bd6e3393640e4f7bbfee26f302ff20","tid":1082531,"uid":3072,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e449e9bc511dd63535f980f48b32a18a75877383","tid":1082531,"uid":49136,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"因為人地有錢去追求完美<br />\n個個都求撚其 可能今日仲係56k上網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:38:18.000Z","msg":"樓主講緊d人追求不切實際既野<br />\n你個立論就係呢種係追求完美既態度<br />\n但「完美」個點根本自己都察覺唔到，咁完美響邊？<br />\n純粹買個心理作用呀？<br />\n<br />\n當你立論成理，同求其有咩關係？<br />\n唔追求完美 = 求其？<br />\n即係我覺得有人買成萬蚊枝水好戇鳩，可以飲貴少少礦泉水就ok，洗乜俾多咁多錢追求一樣自己都分唔到、享受唔到既野<br />\n你就會理解做我好撚求其，再唔幫襯成皮野枝水，呢個世界大家等飲尿呀？<br />\n<br />\non99"},{"pid":"82b0d3a7700272f73a6a618610e933cad0aff0d4","tid":1082531,"uid":229607,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e449e9bc511dd63535f980f48b32a18a75877383","tid":1082531,"uid":49136,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"因為人地有錢去追求完美<br />\n個個都求撚其 可能今日仲係56k上網"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:02:26.000Z","msg":"56k 同100mb 寬頻可以有明顯分別, 你用10分鐘dl 一隻歌同5秒dl 一隻歌無理由分唔到嘛?<br />\n<br />\n但係1ms 同 4ms 肉眼係咪真係分到? 你真係可以留意到千份之3秒既分別?<br />\n<br />\n其實我講漏左既重點係, 之所以我會po 呢個標題, 係因為隔離見到有人買mon, 苦惱緊要ips 既靚色水同可視角好, 定係tn 既ms 反應好, 我就覺得為左打機可以獲得睇唔到既速度分別, 去犧牲明顯既色水分別及可視角, 其實好似有d 鑽牛角尖"},{"pid":"4b3142da40b825f01ab32bc646737af868038388","tid":1082531,"uid":229607,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"1e614fa488c53285750322ce74945bda7429daf1","tid":1082531,"uid":52194,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔夠人打咪瀨呢樣嗰樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"打機輸左其實一定係因為是但以下一種或多種原因:<br />\n1) 對方用左外掛<br />\n2) game dev 設計隻game 有問題<br />\n3) 寬頻廢<br />\n4) 部腦廢<br />\n5) 個mon 廢<br />\n6) keyboard mouse 廢<br />\n7) 張電競椅廢<br />\n8) 天氣太熱/濕/凍/乾<br />\n9) 太陽同月亮以及火星同金星既磁場相互影響下干擾到你<br />\n10) 最衰都係佔中<br />\n<br />\n但就一撚定唔係因為自己廢唔夠人勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17638357465f3f5274e7b74f5796dc5db5d40eb1","tid":1082531,"uid":224565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"電莖嘅嘢我哋識條春咩"},{"pid":"a958789d4f4ca312ad722803239c09c4b849e647","tid":1082531,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"想搭單問...我拎住個144hz mon但隻game低fps, 會唔會格外覺得lag? 應該較低個hz?"},{"pid":"23b8d99b3db4a66211603fc102bce29bf9b06af1","tid":1082531,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a958789d4f4ca312ad722803239c09c4b849e647","tid":1082531,"uid":163758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:57:34.000Z","msg":"想搭單問...我拎住個144hz mon但隻game低fps, 會唔會格外覺得lag? 應該較低個hz?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"換過張顯示卡"},{"pid":"b7ba22d98eac03b841c4382956071