replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"mon嘅反應時間 即係response time<br />\n同input lag係兩樣野黎<br />\nresponse time多數係指每一粒像素由灰轉黑再轉灰嘅時候(GTG)<br />\nresponse time越短 ghosting問題理應越少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">response time並唔係你d畫面delay左幾秒先出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你所講嘅係input lag<br />\n即係由你click開槍 到畫面show到你開槍嘅時間<br />\n依樣野好少廠會有spec list出黎<br />\n只可以靠第三方嘅testing去試<br />\n可以去<a href=\"https://displaylag.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisplaylag.com&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=74df4d9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://displaylag.com</a>睇唔同型號嘅input lag<br />\n<br />\n而多數嘅電視機嘅input lag係長過電腦mon好多好多"},{"pid":"81f4ff6beb98d9501e512ce9c87b036d8bf405b7","tid":1082531,"uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b63aba176aafe59a3fa25d5f4553befa76c2ad49","tid":1082531,"uid":59484,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"mon嘅反應時間 即係response time<br />\n同input lag係兩樣野黎<br />\nresponse time多數係指每一粒像素由灰轉黑再轉灰嘅時候(GTG)<br />\nresponse time越短 ghosting問題理應越少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">response time並唔係你d畫面delay左幾秒先出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你所講嘅係input lag<br />\n即係由你click開槍 到畫面show到你開槍嘅時間<br />\n依樣野好少廠會有spec list出黎<br />\n只可以靠第三方嘅testing去試<br />\n可以去<a href=\"https://displaylag.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisplaylag.com&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=74df4d9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://displaylag.com</a>睇唔同型號嘅input lag<br />\n<br />\n而多數嘅電視機嘅input lag係長過電腦mon好多好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"多謝賜教，我都成日見到GTG呢個Term出現但就唔知係咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n即係我屌錯咗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，input lag 先就係我講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n照你意思即係response time 係由一個像素顏色轉做另一個顏色？我一路以為果D 叫刷新頻率HZ添，又一路以為refresh rate 就已經解部mon 嘅更新畫面反應，i.e. 120hz 即係每秒更新120次，即係8.3ms 一個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅係想學嘢，請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c701d03f0ae022751a2a12ac019c3469e6a2a77","tid":1082531,"uid":59484,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"81f4ff6beb98d9501e512ce9c87b036d8bf405b7","tid":1082531,"uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b63aba176aafe59a3fa25d5f4553befa76c2ad49","tid":1082531,"uid":59484,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"mon嘅反應時間 即係response time<br />\n同input lag係兩樣野黎<br />\nresponse time多數係指每一粒像素由灰轉黑再轉灰嘅時候(GTG)<br />\nresponse time越短 ghosting問題理應越少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">response time並唔係你d畫面delay左幾秒先出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你所講嘅係input lag<br />\n即係由你click開槍 到畫面show到你開槍嘅時間<br />\n依樣野好少廠會有spec list出黎<br />\n只可以靠第三方嘅testing去試<br />\n可以去<a href=\"https://displaylag.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisplaylag.com&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=74df4d9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://displaylag.com</a>睇唔同型號嘅input lag<br />\n<br />\n而多數嘅電視機嘅input lag係長過電腦mon好多好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"多謝賜教，我都成日見到GTG呢個Term出現但就唔知係咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n即係我屌錯咗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，input lag 先就係我講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n照你意思即係response time 係由一個像素顏色轉做另一個顏色？我一路以為果D 叫刷新頻率HZ添，又一路以為refresh rate 就已經解部mon 嘅更新畫面反應，i.e. 120hz 即係每秒更新120次，即係8.3ms 一個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅係想學嘢，請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T00:48:16.000Z","msg":"以120Hz 為例<br />\n每8.3ms會更新一次畫面<br />\n更新下個畫面嘅時候 上一個畫面唔會立即消失<br />\n當你response time係 4ms<br />\n當你用8.3ms時間變左下一個畫面嘅時候<br />\n上一個畫面嘅影像會停留係到大約4ms<br />\n變成左鬼影 ghosting<br />\n所以點解有d mon會有鬼影 就係因為response time長<br />\nresponse time短嘅mon<br />\n配合埋高Hz數 即使係移動緊嘅文字都可以清晰睇到<br />\n你可以上testufo試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCRT mon因為係一條條線用光由左至右上至下射/畫出黎<br />\n即係好似用電筒對牆打橫畫咁<br />\nd光走左就係走左<br />\n所以CRT mon嘅response time係可以少過1 &micro;s"},{"pid":"98f2503c3187efaec610f6abd60c4be7739de27c","tid":1082531,"uid":124785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T00:49:35.000Z","msg":"VA MON 都還可以<br />\n但係反應時間同ips 差唔多不如用番ips<br />\nTN 呢d 十幾年前的板神早要畀人淘汰<br />\n根本係d 廠用黎清舊板同 慳成本而出"},{"pid":"11bf992c9c3baaee7ac435ff0642bbc454fd701f","tid":1082531,"uid":59484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c701d03f0ae022751a2a12ac019c3469e6a2a77","tid":1082531,"uid":59484,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"81f4ff6beb98d9501e512ce9c87b036d8bf405b7","tid":1082531,"uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b63aba176aafe59a3fa25d5f4553befa76c2ad49","tid":1082531,"uid":59484,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:29:18.000Z","msg":"mon嘅反應時間 即係response time<br />\n同input lag係兩樣野黎<br />\nresponse time多數係指每一粒像素由灰轉黑再轉灰嘅時候(GTG)<br />\nresponse time越短 ghosting問題理應越少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">response time並唔係你d畫面delay左幾秒先出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你所講嘅係input lag<br />\n即係由你click開槍 到畫面show到你開槍嘅時間<br />\n依樣野好少廠會有spec list出黎<br />\n只可以靠第三方嘅testing去試<br />\n可以去<a href=\"https://displaylag.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisplaylag.com&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=74df4d9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://displaylag.com</a>睇唔同型號嘅input lag<br />\n<br />\n而多數嘅電視機嘅input lag係長過電腦mon好多好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"多謝賜教，我都成日見到GTG呢個Term出現但就唔知係咩嚟<br />\n<br />\n即係我屌錯咗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，input lag 先就係我講嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n照你意思即係response time 係由一個像素顏色轉做另一個顏色？我一路以為果D 叫刷新頻率HZ添，又一路以為refresh rate 就已經解部mon 嘅更新畫面反應，i.e. 120hz 即係每秒更新120次，即係8.3ms 一個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />